      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk. i was just looking at some old photos today and it hit me. the person in those pictures... they aren't me anymore. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago. now i'm just kind of going through the motions. like a ghost or a walking corpse. just existing.",
